### 张雪峰 AI 咨询 Agent — API 测试集合
### 使用方式：VS Code REST Client 插件 或 HTTPie

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### ==================== 健康检查 ====================

### 根路径
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### 健康检查
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 数据库状态
GET {{baseUrl}}/db/status

### ==================== 对话接口 ====================

### 非流式对话 - 基础查询
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "你好，我是河南考生，560分，理科，能上什么学校？",
  "user_context": {
    "分数": 560,
    "省份": "河南",
    "科类": "理科"
  }
}

### 非流式对话 - 带会话 ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "test-session-001",
  "message": "金融专业就业怎么样？",
  "user_context": {
    "分数": 560,
    "省份": "河南",
    "科类": "理科"
  }
}

### SSE 流式对话
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": "计算机和软件工程哪个好？",
  "stream": true
}

### SSE 流式对话 - 带上下文
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "session_id": "test-session-002",
  "message": "这些学校哪个就业最好？",
  "user_context": {
    "分数": 620,
    "省份": "北京",
    "科类": "理科"
  },
  "stream": true
}

### ==================== 院校查询 ====================

### 按 ID 查询院校
GET {{baseUrl}}/schools/1

### 按名称查询院校
GET {{baseUrl}}/schools/by-name/北京大学

### 查询 985 院校
POST {{baseUrl}}/schools/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "level": "985",
  "page": 1,
  "page_size": 10
}

### 按省份查询院校
POST {{baseUrl}}/schools/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "province": "河南",
  "page": 1,
  "page_size": 20
}

### 模糊搜索院校
POST {{baseUrl}}/schools/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "工业",
  "page": 1,
  "page_size": 20
}

### ==================== 专业查询 ====================

### 按 ID 查询专业
GET {{baseUrl}}/majors/1

### 按名称查询专业
GET {{baseUrl}}/majors/by-name/计算机科学与技术

### 获取热门专业
GET {{baseUrl}}/majors/hot/list?limit=10

### 按学科门类查询
POST {{baseUrl}}/majors/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "工学",
  "page": 1,
  "page_size": 20
}

### 按就业率筛选
POST {{baseUrl}}/majors/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "min_employment_rate": 0.8,
  "page": 1,
  "page_size": 20
}

### ==================== 分数线查询 ====================

### 多条件查询分数线
POST {{baseUrl}}/scores/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "school_name": "清华大学",
  "province": "河南",
  "year": 2025
}

### 按院校查询分数线
GET {{baseUrl}}/scores/school/1?province=河南&year=2025

### 按专业查询分数线
GET {{baseUrl}}/scores/major/1?province=河南&year=2025

### 获取分数统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/scores/stats?school_id=1&province=河南&year=2025

### 按分数范围查询
POST {{baseUrl}}/scores/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "province": "河南",
  "subject_type": "理科",
  "min_score_floor": 550,
  "max_score_ceil": 600,
  "page": 1,
  "page_size": 20
}

### ==================== 招生计划查询 ====================

### 多条件查询招生计划
POST {{baseUrl}}/plans/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "school_name": "清华大学",
  "province": "河南",
  "year": 2025
}

### 按院校查询招生计划
GET {{baseUrl}}/plans/school/1?province=河南&year=2025

### 按专业查询招生计划
GET {{baseUrl}}/plans/major/1?province=河南&year=2025

### ==================== 用户画像 ====================

### 获取用户画像
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile/test-session-001

### 更新用户画像
PUT {{baseUrl}}/profile/test-session-001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "field": "family_background",
  "value": "普通工薪家庭"
}

### 获取追问问题
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile/test-session-001/next-question

### ==================== 会话管理 ====================

### 获取会话信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/session/test-session-001

### 删除会话
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/session/test-session-001

### ==================== 工具定义 ====================

### 获取所有工具定义
GET {{baseUrl}}/tools
